<thisCommand> [<-|+nick!user@host>]

Will add or remove a nick!user@host to/from your server-side silence (ignore) list.

If no nick!user@host is specified, all silences (ignores) are listed.

All silences (ignores) are cleared upon disconnection.

Example(s):
---------------
/<thisCommand>
/<thisCommand> +Bob!*@*
/<thisCommand> -Alice!*@*
